    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so it's basically like the steel handles the pulling forces while the concrete handles the squeezing. what happens if the rebar isn't placed exactly right or if there aren't enough of them? like, does it just fail suddenly or is there a way to see it coming?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
